\subsection*{Ordered List Formatting Options}

The following demonstrates different numbering styles for ordered lists:

\textbf{Arabic numerals (default):}
\begin{enumerate}
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{enumerate}

\textbf{Lowercase letters:}
\begin{enumerate}[label=\alph*)]
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{enumerate}

\textbf{Lowercase Roman numerals:}
\begin{enumerate}[label=\roman*)]
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{enumerate}

\textbf{Uppercase letters:}
\begin{enumerate}[label=\Alph*)]
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{enumerate}

\subsection*{Unordered List Formatting Options}

The following demonstrates different bullet styles for unordered lists:

\textbf{Default bullets:}
\begin{itemize}
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Dashes:}
\begin{itemize}[label=--]
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Asterisks:}
\begin{itemize}[label=$\ast$]
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Custom arrows:}
\begin{itemize}[label=$\rightarrow$]
\item First item
\item Second item
\item Third item
\end{itemize}

